ent-RMCMedalBase = medal
    .desc = A medal.
ent-RMCMedalBronze = bronze medal
    .desc = A bronze medal.
ent-RMCMedalBronzeService = bronze service medal
    .desc = A bronze medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC. It is a very common medal, and is typically the first medal a marine would receive.
ent-RMCMedalSilver = silver medal
    .desc = A silver medal.
ent-RMCMedalSilverService = silver service medal
    .desc = A shiny silver medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC. It is a somewhat common medal which signifies the amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
ent-RMCMedalGold = gold medal
    .desc = A prestigious golden medal.
ent-RMCMedalGoldService = gold service medal
    .desc = A prestigious gold medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC. It signifies the amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
ent-RMCMedalPlatinum = platinum medal
    .desc = An esteemed platinum medal, only able to be handed out by generals due to special circumstances.
ent-RMCMedalPlatinumService = platinum service medal
    .desc = An esteemed platinum medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC. It signifies the sheer amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
ent-RMCMedalRuby = ruby medal
    .desc = An exalted ruby medal, only able to be handed out by Generals due to special circumstances.
ent-RMCMedalRubyService = ruby service medal
    .desc = An Exalted ruby medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC; such medals are hand-given by UNMC Generals directly to a marine. It signifies the excessive amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
ent-RMCMedalEmerald = emerald medal
    .desc = A revered emerald medal, only able to be handed out by High Command due to especially special circumstances.
ent-RMCMedalEmeraldService = emerald service medal
    .desc = A revered emerald awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC; such medals are hand-given by UNMC High Command directly to a marine. It signifies the exorbitant amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
