    .desc = A mythical amethyst medal, only able to be handed out by High Command due to especially special circumstances.
ent-RMCMedalAmethystService = amethyst service medal
    .desc = A mythical amethyst medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC; such medals are hand-given by UNMC High Command directly to a marine. It signifies the unreasonable amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
ent-RMCMedalPrismatic = prismatic medal
    .desc = A mythical prismatic medal, only able to be handed out by High Command due to especially special circumstances.
ent-RMCMedalPrismaticService = prismatic service medal
    .desc = A legendary prismatic medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC, Whom this is awarded may be a god walking amongst mere mortals. It signifies the nigh on impossible amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
